    "_postman_id": "a8f3c210-9b4d-4e1f-8c2a-businexa-api",
    "name": "Businexa API",
    "description": "Local default: `baseUrl` = `http://localhost:5000` (see `PORT` in `.env`).\n\n**Protected routes** expect `Authorization: Bearer <Firebase ID token>`. The `verify-otp` response returns a **custom token** (`firebaseToken`); exchange it with the Firebase client SDK or Identity Toolkit REST API to obtain an **ID token**, then paste it into the `token` variable.\n\n`POST /api/auth/refresh` currently returns 501 (not implemented).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
